{"tid":2145940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情底下，香港依然好撚多on9去行街買衫","createTime":"2020-08-08T09:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T10:47:46.000Z","uid":330847,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b30eacefe6690a132c8c9bbae55426dd4776e3c6","tid":2145940,"uid":330847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:46:50.000Z","msg":"今日星期六，某地方h&amp;m因為執笠，大特價。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母跌到去69宗，個個去躝街買衫。<br />\n<br />\nh&amp;m特價忙撚到呀，好撚心啦，疫情未撚完架，去撚完未呀，係咪覺得自己戴口罩無撚敵左啊，係咪要搞撚到大爆發先滿意啊。<br />\n<br />\n知唔知係個到翻工幾撚驚啊，多人到，屋企冇衫著？係咪一件衫都冇呀屌你老尾😡😡😡😡😡<br />\n一日係咁，一日個疫情都唔撚洗好呀<br />\n多撚謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食撚屎啦你地<br />\n知唔知香港啲醫護幾撚辛苦啊<br />\n出出出出出，出你老母呀屌~~~~~~~~~"},{"pid":"0114331522dfebaa9a666bc5b4db7cd2c1a3131a","tid":2145940,"uid":28960,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:47:32.000Z","msg":"h＆m藍店都幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f903848a6ebd29215c013b612c4e3a63b5ad3832","tid":2145940,"uid":225696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:48:06.000Z","msg":"4000/7000000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d662594f29cc4f3d42951ef5158b5d423a87ba9","tid":2145940,"uid":118647,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩<br />\n咁撚驚你返咩工<br />\n匿係屋企攞老綜啦"},{"pid":"3d668978cf296c422b80aede576e8f4d6528cefe","tid":2145940,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:48:27.000Z","msg":"日日都大把人搶啦<br />\n十幾蚊一件衫<br />\n唔洗著呀"},{"pid":"58072e1769c993fdda5519d4143b8a267af12c6f","tid":2145940,"uid":330847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0114331522dfebaa9a666bc5b4db7cd2c1a3131a","tid":2145940,"uid":28960,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:47:32.000Z","msg":"h＆m藍店都幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020